      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of Oct 10 article about trial of two Libyans charged in bombing of Pan Am Flight 103; description of witness noted</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Because of an editing error, an article yesterday about the trial of two Libyans charged in the bombing of Pan Am Flight 103, which exploded in 1988 over Lockerbie, Scotland, misstated the relationship of a witness to the case. A man depicted in cables by the Central Intelligence Agency as a chronic liar was a central witness for the prosecution, not for the defense. Defense witnesses will not testify until the prosecution concludes its case.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>Because of an editing error, an article yesterday about the trial of two Libyans charged in the bombing of Pan Am Flight 103, which exploded in 1988 over Lockerbie, Scotland, misstated the relationship of a witness to the case. A man depicted in cables by the Central Intelligence Agency as a chronic liar was a central witness for the prosecution, not for the defense. Defense witnesses will not testify until the prosecution concludes its case.</p>
